  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/swS0s2D.png\" width=\"1344\" height=\"576\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Blueprint\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/blueprint\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://tinyurl.com/j9dfktx6\" alt=\"Blueprint\" /></a> <a title=\"Team Abnormals Website\" href=\"https://teamabnormals.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://tinyurl.com/abnormals-disweb\" alt=\"Website\" /></a> <a title=\"Team Abnormals Discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/zADvTSy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/650003402218274816?label=&amp;color=3B3B3B&amp;labelColor=515151&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=Discord&amp;logoColor=DDE4EF\" alt=\"Team Abnormals Discord\" /></a> <a title=\"Team Abnormals Twitter\" href=\"https://twitter.com/teamabnormals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Follow&amp;color=3B3B3B&amp;labelColor=515151&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=Twitter&amp;logoColor=DDE4EF\" alt=\"Team Abnormals Twitter\" /></a> <a title=\"Team Abnormals Patreon\" href=\"https://www.patreon.com/teamabnormals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?label=&amp;color=3B3B3B&amp;labelColor=515151&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=Patreon&amp;logoColor=DDE4EF&amp;url=https://shieldsio-patreon.vercel.app/api/?username=teamabnormals&amp;type=patrons\" alt=\"Patreon\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Swamp Expansion has been discontinued, as it has been merged into <a style=\"font-size: 20px;\" href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/environmental\">Environmental</a>!</strong></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eP0EGgU.png\" width=\"1344\" height=\"48\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>📖 About:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Swamps are really cool, don't you think? There's witch huts, slimes... and not much more. And we don't like that. <br /> This mod adds a new wood type which replaces swamp oaks - willow. In Swamps you will also find a new creature called the Slabfish, which can be used as a friend and to store items by giving it a backpack! The mod also adds cattails to swamps and adds large mushrooms into swamps for Minecraft: Bedrock Edition parity! On top of that, there are mud bricks - and much more to come, including Mud Pools and more Swamp creatures &amp; variants!</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eP0EGgU.png\" width=\"1344\" height=\"48\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>📦 Cross-Compatibility:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"Boatload\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/boatload\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Boatload</span></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Buzzier Bees\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/buzzier-bees\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Buzzier Bees</span></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Quark\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/quark\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Quark</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eP0EGgU.png\" width=\"1344\" height=\"48\" /></p>\n<p><a title=\"Nodecraft\" href=\"https://nodecraft.com/r/abnormals\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oZS1R9g.png\" width=\"1280\" height=\"184\" /></a></p>",
